imit)\n- **tower-resilience-retry**: `retry`, `middleware`, `resilience`, `tower`, `backoff`\n- **tower-resilience-ratelimiter**: `rate-limit`, `middleware`, `resilience`, `tower`, `throttle`\n- **tower-resilience-bulkhead**: `tower`, `bulkhead`, `resilience`, `isolation`, `concurrency`\n\n### Dependency Improvements\n- Updated tokio workspace dependency from `\"1\"` to precise version `\"1.47.1\"`\n- Prevents unexpected old versions when using the `minimal-versions` flag\n- Recommended by lib.rs for more reliable dependency resolution\n\n## Impact\n\nThese metadata improvements will:\n- \u2705 Help users find the crates through better categorization on crates.io and lib.rs\n- \u2705 Improve search results with relevant keywords\n- \u2705 Ensure consistent tokio version resolution across the workspace\n- \u2705 Remove warnings from lib.rs dashboard\n\n## Testing\n\n- `cargo fmt --all` \u2705\n- `cargo clippy --all-targets --all-features -- -D warnings` \u2705\n\nNo functional changes, only Cargo.toml metadata.", "created_at": "2025-10-13T16:40:08Z", "updated_at": "2025-10-13T18:12:26Z", "closed_at": "2025-10-13T18:12:24Z", "merged_at": "2025-10-13T18:12:24Z", "merge_commit_sha": "a4d860e50f6cdf507696b479656fdac22ba452b3", "assignee": null, "assignees": [], "requested_reviewers": [], "requested_teams": [], "labels": [], "milestone": null, "draft": false, "commits_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/joshrotenberg/tower-resilience/pulls/120/commits", "review_comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/joshrotenberg/tower-resilience/pulls/120/comments", "review_comment_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/joshrotenberg/tower-resilience/pulls/comments{/number}", "comments_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/joshrotenberg/tower-resilience/issues/120/comments", "statuses_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/joshrotenberg/tower-resilience/statuses/e2f129bde5b3d2f77e9ba8ecb9dc365557a2657e", "head": {"label": "joshrotenberg:chore/add-crate-metadata", "ref": "chore/add-crate-me